    • getSigma

      double getSigma(int v)
      Return the error (or sigma value) of this node in the neural network. Phi is dependent on the result prodced by the neural network with respect to the acctual value of the result in t.

    • update

      void update(int v)
      When called all elements preceeding the one this is called on will be trained be getting a sigma value from the next element, computing their sigma value, and calling update on the previous node.
      Parameters:
      v - - v is the version of the neural net state. If the node has a different version recorded for its sigma value, it will recompute it. If the versions match, then no recomputation is necessary.
